# NAME
. whoami(1) - print effective user ID

# SYNOPSIS
$ whoami [OPTION]...

# DESCRIPTION
. Print the user name associated with the current effective user ID.
  Same as `id -un`.

# EXAMPLES
. Show current user:
$ whoami
